            <head>THE DAY-BREAKERS</head>
            <lg>
               <l enjamb="yes">We are not come to wage a strife</l>
               <l enjamb="no">With swords upon this hill,</l>
               <l enjamb="yes">It is not wise to waste the life</l>
               <l enjamb="no">Against a stubborn will.</l>
               <l enjamb="no">Yet would we die as some have done.</l>
               <l enjamb="no">Beating a way for the rising sun.</l>
            </lg>
            <byline>-Arna Bontemps</byline>
         </div>
      </body>
